# E-SYSTEM Programming Rules
# Standard: P.A.R.A. + ISO-SAGE

- Language: Python 3.12+
- Hierarchy: P.A.R.A. (00_SOPORTE, 01_SRC, 02_TESTS, 03_DOCS, 04_ASSETS)
- Nomenclature: CLAW_YYYY_MM_DD_DESCRIPTION_VXX.py
- Independence: Config in 00_SOPORTE, Logic in 01_SRC.
- Physical Security: Log 'alerta de enfriamiento' if execution exceeds 50 minutes.
- Style: Clean code, ISO-SAGE comments.
- IA Coordination: Sage (qwen2.5:0.5b) coordinates with specialized agents. Claude excluded.
